{quote}
Vinod Kumar Vavilapalli, have you had any chance to think about the implementation for this feature (in-queue preemption). We are seeing cases where we have an ad-hoc queue that many people can use, bu long-running containers are using up many resources in that queue and keeping other users' apps from starting.
